title: Frank Clark Trade, Draft's Most Interesting Teams Part 2 (Football 4/24)
description:
Will Brinson and John Breech break down the biggest news of the day, including the Frank Clark trade from the Seahawks to the Chiefs. And then Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson to look at three more of the most interesting teams in the NFL Draft.
